{"data":[{"date":"15:57 13/11","title":"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: HLV Eriksson c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 canh b\u1ea1c c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Philippines?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/goc-nhin-hlv-eriksson-co-phai-canh-bac-cua-bong-da-philippines.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a \u0110T Philippines \u1edf s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i AFF Cup 2018, t\u1edd ESPN \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Eriksson c\u1ee7a L\u0110B\u0110 Philippines ch\u1eb3ng kh\u00e1c n\u00e0o m\u1ed9t canh b\u1ea1c. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00fang?\r\n\r\n</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 16.5pt;\">\u00a0</p>\r\n<h2><br>\r\n\u201cHLV Sven-Goran Eriksson l\u00e0 canh b\u1ea1c c\u1ee7a Philippines\u201d<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 c\u00e2y vi\u1ebft\u00a0John Duerden c\u1ee7a\u00a0ESPN nh\u1eafc t\u1edbi trong m\u1ed9t ph\u00f3ng s\u1ef1 n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u0110T Philippines \u1edf k\u1ef3 AFF Cup 2018. \u1ede gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay, L\u0110B\u0110 Philippines (PFF) \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t c\u00fa s\u1ed1c l\u1edbn khi chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n t\u1eebng d\u1eabn d\u1eaft nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi nh\u01b0 \u0110T Anh, Mexico hay CLB Manchester City v\u1ec1 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u0129 nhi\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n n\u0103m nay \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 70 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, PFF c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, theo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00e0 80 ngh\u00ecn \u0111\u00f4 la M\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1ea3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00e0ng th\u00e1ng, ch\u01b0a k\u00e8m ph\u1ee5 c\u1ea5p.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Eriksson c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i canh b\u1ea1c c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Philippines h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Eriksson c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i canh b\u1ea1c c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Philippines h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/bi-lang-quen-tai-philippines-hlv-eriksson-noi-gi.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>ESPN nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh L\u0110B\u0110 Philippines \u0111ang ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t canh b\u1ea1c mang t\u00ean\u00a0Eriksson</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t con s\u1ed1 \u201cr\u1ea5t kh\u1ee7ng\u201d so v\u1edbi m\u1eb7t b\u1eb1ng chung \u1edf khu v\u1ef1c \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1, khi m\u00e0 c\u1ea3 HLV Park Hang Seo hay \u00f4ng Milovan Rajevac c\u1ee7a \u0110T Th\u00e1i Lan c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi 20 ngh\u00ecn \u0111\u00f4 la M\u1ef9.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi \u0111\u1eadm cho HLV Eriksson, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Philippines \u0111ang ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t v\u00e1n b\u1ea1c li\u1ec1u l\u0129nh. V\u00e0 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 cho th\u1ea5y n\u00f3 s\u1ebd th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p>\u00a0</o:p></p>\r\n<h2>D\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">ESPN \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh: \"Vi\u1ec7c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Eriksson tr\u00ean kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd \u0111em l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng r\u1ee7i ro n\u1ebfu nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o th\u00e0nh t\u00edch kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Eriksson c\u00e0ng v\u1ec1 sau c\u00e0ng c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111i xu\u1ed1ng. Sau khi chia tay \u0110T Anh n\u0103m 2006, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n \u1edf r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb Manchester City cho t\u1edbi Mexico, \u0111\u1ebfn B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0, r\u1ed3i Leicester City\u2026 Song t\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n n\u00e0y, v\u1ecb c\u1ef1u thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Tam S\u01b0 \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn HLV Eriksson c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 canh b\u1ea1c c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Philippines h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn HLV Eriksson c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 canh b\u1ea1c c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Philippines h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/10/9/Goc-nhin-HLV-Eriksson-co-phai-la-canh-bac-cua-bong-da-Philippines-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>S\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a HLV Eriksson ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng \u0111i xu\u1ed1ng sau khi chia tay \u0110T Anh</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau nh\u1eefng n\u0103m th\u00e1ng c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i tr\u1eddi \u00c2u, HLV Eriksson chuy\u1ec3n sang d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Trung Qu\u1ed1c nh\u01b0 Qu\u1ea3ng Ch\u00e2u R&F, Th\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u1ea3i SIPG hay Th\u00e2m Quy\u1ebfn FC. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 'mi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea5t h\u1ee9a' \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n sinh n\u0103m 1948 ph\u00e1t huy h\u1ebft n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ebf n\u00ean khi chuy\u1ec3n sang d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110T Philippines, vi\u1ec7c HLV Eriksson ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u0169ng l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 x\u1ea3y ra, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u1edbi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/\" target=\"_blank\">b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 </span>\u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Qu\u1ef9 th\u1eddi gian \u00edt \u1ecfi n\u1eafm quy\u1ec1n ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o \u1edf \u0110T Philippines s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n trong vi\u1ec7c t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh t\u00edch l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft m\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u1ec1n nhi\u1ec7m nh\u01b0 Simon McMenemy, Michael Weiss\u00a0hay Tom Dooley \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-viet-nam-vs-philippines-aff-suzuki-cup-2010-478-201493.html\" style=\"background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Vi\u1ec7t Nam 0-2 Philippines (b\u1ea3ng B AFF Suzuki Cup 2010)</span>\u00a0</o:p></p>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng Eriksson v\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m tin c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Philippines<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u0111ang nghi ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a HLV Eriksson t\u1ea1i Philippines nh\u01b0ng \u1edf\u00a0m\u1ed9t kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean PFF s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eddi n\u00e0o phung ph\u00ed ti\u1ec1n b\u1ea1c \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eddi m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb HLV \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ebft th\u1eddi v\u1ec1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u1edf 2 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn m\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y s\u1eafp tham d\u1ef1 g\u1ed3m <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/aff-cup-c334-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">AFF Cup 2018</span> v\u00e0 Asian Cup 2019.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf th\u00ec s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a v\u1ecb c\u1ef1u thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Tam s\u01b0 \u0111ang mang t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin l\u1edbn cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Philippines, gi\u00fap h\u1ecd v\u1eefng t\u00e2m thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean chinh ph\u1ee5c chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap b\u1ea1c AFF Cup.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Eriksson\" title=\"HLV Eriksson\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/11/13/hlv-eriksson-than-trong-truoc-lan-cam-quan-dau-tien-tai-philippines.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Eriksson \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ef1a tinh th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0110T Philippines h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi danh hi\u1ec7u AFF Cup</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi \u00f4ng Eriksson tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 bi\u1ec7t danh \u201cThe Azkals\u201d, \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t l\u00e0n s\u00f3ng nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eeb n\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Philippines \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec m\u00e0u c\u1edd s\u1eafc \u00e1o v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n danh ti\u1ebfng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn Neil Etheridge, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 28 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed1i \u0111a 3 tr\u1eadn v\u1edbi \u0110TQG v\u00ec c\u00f2n b\u1ecb r\u00e0ng bu\u1ed9c v\u1edbi Cardiff. Nh\u01b0ng anh r\u1ea5t khao kh\u00e1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00f3p s\u1ee9c c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i chinh ph\u1ee5c chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap m\u00e0u b\u1ea1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, HLV Eriksson t\u1eebng su\u00fdt t\u1ea1o n\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u th\u1ea7n k\u00ec khi d\u1eabn d\u1eaft B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 \u1edf World Cup 2010. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn xa, nh\u01b0ng B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 c\u1ee7a Eriksson khi \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng khi\u1ebfn B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Brazil ph\u1ea3i v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3. D\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sven-Goran Eriksson, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u Phi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng th\u1ea5y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Do v\u1eady, tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1edd b\u00f3ng l\u0103n, kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u1ec7u HLV Goran Eriksson s\u1ebd th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Philippines. \u201cThe Azkals\u201d \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t d\u00e0n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0m n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a HLV Eriksson \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 16.5pt; text-align: justify;\"><em><u>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n</u></em><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/nhan-dinh-bong-da/philippines-vs-singapore-19h00-ngay-1311-aff-cup-2018-344-202167.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/11/13/philippines-vs-singapore-19h00-ngay-1311-aff-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/nhan-dinh-bong-da/philippines-vs-singapore-19h00-ngay-1311-aff-cup-2018-344-202167.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Philippines vs Singapore 19h00 ng\u00e0y 13/11 (AFF Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nNh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay Philippines vs Singapore l\u00fac 19h00 ng\u00e0y 13/11 (B\u1ea3ng B AFF Cup 2018): \u00dd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/aff-cup-2018/hlv-eriksson-than-trong-truoc-lan-cam-quan-dau-tien-tai-philippines-334-202147.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/11/13/hlv-eriksson-than-trong-truoc-lan-cam-quan-dau-tien-tai-philippines.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/aff-cup-2018/hlv-eriksson-than-trong-truoc-lan-cam-quan-dau-tien-tai-philippines-334-202147.html\">HLV Eriksson th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1ea7n c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i Philippines</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110T Philippines, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi Goran Eriksson \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng khi n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/aff-cup-2018/dt-philippines-mat-nhan-to-quan-trong-truoc-tran-ra-quan-tai-aff-cup-2018-334-202093.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/11/12/Javier-Patino-Philippines-national-team-2015-FIA-Sports-Management-710x399.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/aff-cup-2018/dt-philippines-mat-nhan-to-quan-trong-truoc-tran-ra-quan-tai-aff-cup-2018-334-202093.html\">\u0110T Philippines m\u1ea5t nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i AFF Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nTheo tin v\u1eeba nh\u1eadn, \u0110T Philippines s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Patino \u1edf AFF Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/aff-cup-2018/thu-mon-neil-etheridge-co-kha-nang-chi-bat-toi-da-hai-tran-334-202091.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/10/12/thu-mon-neil-etheridge-co-kha-nang-chi-bat-toi-da-hai-tran.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/aff-cup-2018/thu-mon-neil-etheridge-co-kha-nang-chi-bat-toi-da-hai-tran-334-202091.html\">Tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb Anh, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Philippines c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n n\u1ebfu g\u1eb7p Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nBay t\u1eeb Anh v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ef1 AFF Cup 2018 nh\u01b0ng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Neil Etheridge c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n t\u1ed1i \u0111a hai tr\u1eadn n\u1ebfu Philippines kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/aff-cup-2018/bi-lang-quen-tai-philippines-hlv-eriksson-noi-gi-334-201946.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/bi-lang-quen-tai-philippines-hlv-eriksson-noi-gi.PNG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/aff-cup-2018/bi-lang-quen-tai-philippines-hlv-eriksson-noi-gi-334-201946.html\">B\u1ecb \u201cl\u00e3ng qu\u00ean\u201d t\u1ea1i Philippines, HLV Eriksson n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span><br>\r\nNh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, HLV Eriksson \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh sau khi kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n n\u1ed3ng h\u1eadu t\u1ea1i Philippines.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/aff-cup-2018/thu-quan-philippines-dat-muc-tieu-khung-o-aff-cup-2018-334-201945.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/11/11/thu-quan-philippines-dat-muc-tieu-khung-o-aff-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/aff-cup-2018/thu-quan-philippines-dat-muc-tieu-khung-o-aff-cup-2018-334-201945.html\">Th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n Philippines \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng \u1edf AFF Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf AFF Cup 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Philippines, Phil Younghusband \u0111\u00e3 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 s\u1ebd v\u00e0o t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; line-height: 115%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:\n18.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5606","checkdouble":"202185"},{"date":"16:23 13/11","title":"HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n Chelsea mua b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c sao tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/25/hlv-sarri-muon-chelsea-mua-bang-duoc-nabil-fekir.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Nabil Fekir c\u1ee7a Lyon v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m 2019, theo The Sun, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n HLV Maurizio Sarri mu\u1ed1n The Blues \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.\r\n</h2><h2>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Sarri v\u1eabn \u0111ang ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, song h\u1ecd v\u1eabn g\u1eb7p m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ghi b\u00e0n. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi Everton, The Blues \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-0, tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi BATE \u1edf Europa League nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng 1-0.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Nabil Fekir v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m 2019 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Nabil Fekir v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m 2019 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/11/12/Chelsea-muon-mua-Nabil-Fekir-vao-thang-1-nam-2019-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Maurizio Sarri mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Chelsea l\u00fac n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng duy tr\u00ec s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh. B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Morata v\u00e0 Giroud tr\u1eadn n\u1ed5 tr\u1eadn x\u1ecbt, nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 Willian hay Pedro c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng n\u1ed5 s\u00fang \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n. Chelsea \u0111ang ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o Eden Hazard.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh, HLV Sarri \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m 2019. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Pedro v\u00e0 Willian \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 l\u1edbn tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nChelsea quan t\u00e2m Fekir</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Nabil Fekir c\u1ee7a Lyon v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m 2019, theo The Sun, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n HLV Maurizio Sarri mu\u1ed1n The Blues \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n Chelsea mua b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c sao tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n Chelsea mua b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c sao tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/30/HLV-Sarri-muon-Chelsea-mua-bang-duoc-sao-tuyen-Phap-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea quan t\u00e2m Nabil Fekir\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNabil Fekir \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Lyon, m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc anh ghi t\u1edbi 24 b\u00e0n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 4 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o sau 10 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf Ligue 1 v\u00e0 Champions League.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111a n\u0103ng, ngo\u00e0i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh anh c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng hay trung phong \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/nabil-fekir-bat-den-xanh-cho-chelsea-va-bayern-munich-172-201731.html\" target=\"_blank\"><em><u>Nabil Fekir t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Lyon</u></em></span>, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 cho th\u1ea5y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chi ra \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 55 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u1edbi hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Lyon, ngo\u00e0i The Blues th\u00ec Bayern Munich c\u0169ng \u0111ang quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5605","checkdouble":"202186"},{"date":"17:44 13/11","title":"Andreas Christensen kh\u00f4ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Chelsea nh\u01b0ng...","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/18/andreas-christensen-thua-nhan-khong-hai-long-voi-hlv-sarri.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Antonin Panenka ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Sergio Ramos. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi khai s\u00e1ng ra ki\u1ec3u \u0111\u00e1 penalty n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o khi h\u1eadu b\u1ed1i th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch thu\u1ea7n th\u1ee5c.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Panenka khai s\u00e1ng ki\u1ec3u \u0111\u00e1 penalty</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAntonin Panenka t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0110T Ti\u1ec7p Kh\u1eafc v\u00e0o giai \u0111o\u1ea1n n\u0103m 1973 t\u1edbi 1982. C\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng sinh n\u0103m 1948 nay l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch CLB Bohemians Praha, n\u01a1i \u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 g\u1eafn b\u00f3 trong nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m. Trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, Panenka \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft t\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 penalty \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eddi \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Euro 1976 v\u1edbi T\u00e2y \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i Belgrade.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m, Panenka c\u00f3 c\u00fa b\u1ea5m b\u00f3ng th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o gi\u1eefa khung th\u00e0nh khi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng Sepp Maier \u0111\u00e3 bay v\u1ec1 b\u00ean tr\u00e1i. K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3, ki\u1ec3u \u0111\u00e1 penalty c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Ti\u1ec7p Kh\u1eafc \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi sao ch\u00e9p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Antonin Panenka ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Sergio Ramos v\u00e0 ki\u1ec3u \u0111\u00e1 penalty h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Antonin Panenka ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Sergio Ramos v\u00e0 ki\u1ec3u \u0111\u00e1 penalty h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/11/13/antonin-panenka-phat-bieu-ve-sergio-ramos.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ramos th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n ki\u1ec3u \u0111\u00e1 Panenka</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nKhen ng\u1ee3i Ramos</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n penalty ki\u1ec3u Panenka n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng nh\u1ea5t ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn Sergio Ramos. M\u1edbi cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n qua, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Real \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m tung l\u01b0\u1edbi Celta Vigo v\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem l\u1ea1i c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 penalty ki\u1ec3u Panenka c\u1ee7a Ramos tr\u01b0\u1edbc Celta:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/11/12/real-83.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n</strong><br>\r\nAntonin Panenka ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Sergio Ramos tr\u00ean t\u1edd AS. Ti\u1ec1n b\u1ed1i 69 tu\u1ed5i t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0 \u0111ang l\u00e0m. \u201c<em>T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng Ramos th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n penalty theo phong c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u n\u00f3i nh\u01b0 v\u1eady</em>\u201d, Panenka chia s\u1ebb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c<em>N\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i nh\u1edb l\u1ea1i k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m t\u1eeb Belgrade n\u0103m 1976. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Nh\u1eefng k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c \u1edbn l\u1ea1nh! T\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o r\u1eb1ng Ramos \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n m\u1ed9t ki\u1ec3u \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nhi\u1ec1u danh th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c.</em>\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c<em>Ramos ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. \u0110\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ki\u1ec3u \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng. T\u00f4i nh\u1edb nh\u1eefng l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c nh\u1ea5t, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec1u tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t.</em>\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c<em>C\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Celta l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 Panenka th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft nh\u1ea5t t\u00f4i t\u1eebng th\u1ea5y \u1edf Ramos. T\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t th\u00edch v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao n\u00f3. M\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, kh\u00f4ng nghi ng\u1edd g\u00ec n\u1eefa.</em>\u201d <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Real Madrid tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/du-am-viktoria-plzen-05-real-madrid-cuoc-hon-phoi-tot-dep-giua-184-201686.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/11/8/thang-lon-sao-real-muon-hlv-tam-quyen-o-lai.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/du-am-viktoria-plzen-05-real-madrid-cuoc-hon-phoi-tot-dep-giua-184-201686.html\">Real Madrid l\u1ea1i th\u1eafng: Cu\u1ed9c h\u00f4n ph\u1ed1i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p gi\u1eefa Viking v\u00e0 \u1ea4n \u0110\u1ed9</span><br>\r\n<span>Real Madrid th\u1eddi Santiago Solari v\u1eabn \u0111ang ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e1ng n\u1ec3 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. H\u1ecd m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Viktoria Plzen \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn to\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u00ean con s\u1ed1 3.</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/celta-vigo-vs-real-madrid-vong-12-la-liga-201819-hom-nay-372-202027.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/11/10/celta-vigo-vs-real-madrid-vong-12-la-liga-201819-hom-nay.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/celta-vigo-vs-real-madrid-vong-12-la-liga-201819-hom-nay-372-202027.html\">Celta 2-4 Real Madrid (KT): Tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a HLV t\u1ea1m quy\u1ec1n Solari kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i b\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng</span><br>\r\n<span>HLV t\u1ea1m quy\u1ec1n Solari ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cho th\u1ea5y c\u00e1i duy\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi Real khi c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec m\u1ea1ch chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Celta \u1edf v\u00f2ng...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5604","checkdouble":"202187"},{"date":"16:04 13/11","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Philippines vs Singapore 19h00 ng\u00e0y 13/11 (AFF Cup 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/11/13/philippines-vs-singapore-aff-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Philippines vs Singapore: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Philippines vs Singapore b\u1ea3ng B AFF Cup 2018 l\u00fac 19h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 13/11.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n Indonesia \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n nh\u01b0ng Singapore \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. HLV Fandi Ahmad, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u1ed1 1 qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ea3o s\u01b0 t\u1eed, \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa s\u1ee9c tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0111a d\u1ea1ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7y hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c v\u00e0 tu\u00e2n th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Singapore th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Indonesia.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Philippines vs Singapore t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 AFF Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Philippines vs Singapore t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 AFF Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/11/13/155747-Philippines-vs-Singapore.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Philippines vs Singapore</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ef1c ra chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i c\u1ee7a Singapore kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 may m\u1eafn, m\u00e0 n\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3 t\u1eeb c\u1ea3 qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb chu \u0111\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1ea3i. Singapore \u0111\u00e3 5 tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, trong \u0111\u00f3 th\u1eafng t\u1edbi 4. \u1ede chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, Philippines c\u0169ng \u0111\u1eb7t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1ea5t cao \u1edf gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 khu v\u1ef1c. \u0110\u00e2y m\u1edbi l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd t\u1ea1i AFF Cup 2018 do l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n, h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPhilippines \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh tay khi m\u1eddi HLV l\u00e3o l\u00e0ng Sven-Goran Eriksson t\u1eebng l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u1edf c\u00e1c CLB l\u1edbn v\u00e0 \u0110TQG h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u1ec1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft. V\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1, sau qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng tuy\u1ec3n Philippines \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c CLB t\u1ea1i Premier League, Cardiff ch\u1ea5p thu\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Neil Etheridge v\u1ec1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 \u0110TQG. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n Philippines c\u00f2n c\u00f3 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c mang g\u1ed1c g\u00e1c Philippines \u0111ang ch\u01a1i cho c\u00e1c CLB n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Philippines kh\u00f3 co th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u0103n \u00fd c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft khi m\u00e0 th\u1eddi gian t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng nhau qu\u00e1 \u00edt. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, HLV Eriksson d\u00f9 th\u1eeba kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 n\u1eafm b\u1eaft ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1eb7c th\u00f9 ri\u00eang bi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1. Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n n\u00e0y c\u0169ng b\u1ecb nghi ng\u1edd b\u1edfi qu\u00e1 c\u1ed5 \u0111i\u1ec3n v\u00e0 l\u1ea1c h\u1eadu so v\u1edbi th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPhilippines t\u1eebng ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Singapore ngay t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 AFF Cup \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0o n\u0103m 1996, v\u00e0 thua tr\u1eafng 3 b\u00e0n. 5 l\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfp theo, h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u b\u00f3 tay trong vi\u1ec7c t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm ph\u1ea7n th\u1eafng (thua 2. C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 2 n\u0103m, 2 \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169ng t\u1eebng g\u1eb7p nhau \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng AFF Cup 2016 v\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-0.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5603","checkdouble":"202188"},{"date":"16:08 13/11","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Indonesia vs \u0110\u00f4ng Timor 19h00 ng\u00e0y 13/11 (AFF Cup 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/11/13/indonesia-vs-dong-timor-aff-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Indonesia vs \u0110\u00f4ng Timor: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Indonesia vs Timor Leste b\u1ea3ng B AFF Cup 2018 l\u00fac 19h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 13/11.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)<br>\r\n<br>\r\nIndonesia d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 5 l\u1ea7n l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft AFF Cup nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n \u0111\u0103ng quang \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. T\u1ea1i AFF Cup 2016, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 v\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea3o c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n s\u1ed1 1 khu v\u1ef1c, Th\u00e1i Lan. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, nh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ec7 Indonesia v\u1eabn \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch AFF Cup 2018 ho\u1eb7c \u00edt nh\u1ea5t ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf chung k\u1ebft.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Indonesia vs \u0110\u00f4ng Timor AFF Suzuki Cup 2018 h\u00f4m nay h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Indonesia vs \u0110\u00f4ng Timor AFF Suzuki Cup 2018 h\u00f4m nay h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/11/13/indonesia-vs-timor-leste-19h00-ngay-1311-aff-cup-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Indonesia vs Timor Leste</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Indonesia s\u1edbm b\u1ecb d\u1ed9i g\u00e1o n\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1ea1nh, khi tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Singapore. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 y\u1ebfu h\u01a1n. Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi Indonesia s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea1nh tranh 2 t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft b\u1edfi ngo\u00e0i Singapore, b\u1ea3ng B c\u00f2n Philippines v\u00e0 Th\u00e1i Lan th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea3o qu\u1ed1c s\u01b0 t\u1eed v\u1eeba \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i h\u1ecd. Nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft c\u1ee7a Indonesia l\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0110\u00f4ng Timor, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTimor Leste l\u00e0 qu\u1ed1c gia non tr\u1ebb nh\u1ea5t khu v\u1ef1c \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 n\u00ean n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea5t y\u1ebfu c\u0169ng k\u00e9m ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n. \u0110\u00f4ng Timor ch\u1ec9 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i AFF Cup t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2004 nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n duy nh\u1ea5t h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u01b0\u1edbc AFF Cup 2018 b\u1edfi c\u00e1c n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng qua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i. Kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00ec th\u1ebf v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Timor Leste r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n, Timor Leste d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng b\u1ecb Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u00e8 b\u1eb9p 7 b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng g\u1ee1 d\u00f9 nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1n qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ee9c. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n m\u00e0 Timor Leste th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n l\u00e0 v\u00f4 cung h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng d\u00e0nh cho Indonesia g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, b\u1edfi tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n gi\u1eefa \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean qu\u00e1 ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch, ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m cao c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nhf. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Bima Sakti th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n ra sao, gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o. Trong l\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Timor Leste, Indonesia \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-0.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5602","checkdouble":"202189"},{"date":"16:52 13/11","title":"\u201cVua Panenka\u201d l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng khen ng\u1ee3i h\u1eadu b\u1ed1i Sergio Ramos","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/11/13/antonin-panenka-phat-bieu-ve-sergio-ramos.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Antonin Panenka ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Sergio Ramos. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi khai s\u00e1ng ra ki\u1ec3u \u0111\u00e1 penalty n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o khi h\u1eadu b\u1ed1i th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch thu\u1ea7n th\u1ee5c.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Panenka khai s\u00e1ng ki\u1ec3u \u0111\u00e1 penalty</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAntonin Panenka t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0110T Ti\u1ec7p Kh\u1eafc v\u00e0o giai \u0111o\u1ea1n n\u0103m 1973 t\u1edbi 1982. C\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng sinh n\u0103m 1948 nay l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch CLB Bohemians Praha, n\u01a1i \u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 g\u1eafn b\u00f3 trong nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m. Trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, Panenka \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft t\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 penalty \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eddi \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Euro 1976 v\u1edbi T\u00e2y \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i Belgrade.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m, Panenka c\u00f3 c\u00fa b\u1ea5m b\u00f3ng th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o gi\u1eefa khung th\u00e0nh khi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng Sepp Maier \u0111\u00e3 bay v\u1ec1 b\u00ean tr\u00e1i. K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3, ki\u1ec3u \u0111\u00e1 penalty c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Ti\u1ec7p Kh\u1eafc \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi sao ch\u00e9p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Antonin Panenka ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Sergio Ramos v\u00e0 ki\u1ec3u \u0111\u00e1 penalty h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Antonin Panenka ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Sergio Ramos v\u00e0 ki\u1ec3u \u0111\u00e1 penalty h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/11/13/antonin-panenka-phat-bieu-ve-sergio-ramos.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ramos th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n ki\u1ec3u \u0111\u00e1 Panenka</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nKhen ng\u1ee3i Ramos</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n penalty ki\u1ec3u Panenka n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng nh\u1ea5t ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn Sergio Ramos. M\u1edbi cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n qua, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Real \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m tung l\u01b0\u1edbi Celta Vigo v\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem l\u1ea1i c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 penalty ki\u1ec3u Panenka c\u1ee7a Ramos tr\u01b0\u1edbc Celta:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/11/12/real-83.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n</strong><br>\r\nAntonin Panenka ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Sergio Ramos tr\u00ean t\u1edd AS. Ti\u1ec1n b\u1ed1i 69 tu\u1ed5i t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0 \u0111ang l\u00e0m. \u201c<em>T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng Ramos th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n penalty theo phong c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u n\u00f3i nh\u01b0 v\u1eady</em>\u201d, Panenka chia s\u1ebb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c<em>N\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i nh\u1edb l\u1ea1i k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m t\u1eeb Belgrade n\u0103m 1976. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Nh\u1eefng k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c \u1edbn l\u1ea1nh! T\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o r\u1eb1ng Ramos \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n m\u1ed9t ki\u1ec3u \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nhi\u1ec1u danh th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c.</em>\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c<em>Ramos ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. \u0110\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ki\u1ec3u \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng. T\u00f4i nh\u1edb nh\u1eefng l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c nh\u1ea5t, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec1u tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t.</em>\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c<em>C\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Celta l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 Panenka th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft nh\u1ea5t t\u00f4i t\u1eebng th\u1ea5y \u1edf Ramos. T\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t th\u00edch v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao n\u00f3. M\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, kh\u00f4ng nghi ng\u1edd g\u00ec n\u1eefa.</em>\u201d <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Real Madrid tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/du-am-viktoria-plzen-05-real-madrid-cuoc-hon-phoi-tot-dep-giua-184-201686.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/11/8/thang-lon-sao-real-muon-hlv-tam-quyen-o-lai.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/du-am-viktoria-plzen-05-real-madrid-cuoc-hon-phoi-tot-dep-giua-184-201686.html\">Real Madrid l\u1ea1i th\u1eafng: Cu\u1ed9c h\u00f4n ph\u1ed1i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p gi\u1eefa Viking v\u00e0 \u1ea4n \u0110\u1ed9</span><br>\r\n<span>Real Madrid th\u1eddi Santiago Solari v\u1eabn \u0111ang ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e1ng n\u1ec3 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. H\u1ecd m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Viktoria Plzen \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn to\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u00ean con s\u1ed1 3.</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/celta-vigo-vs-real-madrid-vong-12-la-liga-201819-hom-nay-372-202027.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/11/10/celta-vigo-vs-real-madrid-vong-12-la-liga-201819-hom-nay.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/celta-vigo-vs-real-madrid-vong-12-la-liga-201819-hom-nay-372-202027.html\">Celta 2-4 Real Madrid (KT): Tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a HLV t\u1ea1m quy\u1ec1n Solari kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i b\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng</span><br>\r\n<span>HLV t\u1ea1m quy\u1ec1n Solari ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cho th\u1ea5y c\u00e1i duy\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi Real khi c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec m\u1ea1ch chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Celta \u1edf v\u00f2ng...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5601","checkdouble":"202191"},{"date":"17:16 13/11","title":"Si\u00eau th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/11/13/thu-mon-alisson-nhan-xet-ve-phong-do.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ea1i Liverpool. Anh th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00fac n\u00e0o c\u0169ng su\u00f4n s\u1ebb, nh\u01b0ng \u0111ang nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o t\u1ea1i CLB m\u1edbi.</h2><h2><br>\r\nAlisson \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Liverpool b\u1ecf t\u1edbi 72.5 tri\u1ec7u euro (65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng) \u0111\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 Alisson t\u1eeb AS Roma. \u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi d\u00e0nh cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1ecb Chelsea ph\u00e1 v\u1edbi th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Kepa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAlisson gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool mang theo nhi\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc anh, b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Simon Mignolet v\u00e0 Loris Karius khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 ph\u1eadp ph\u00f9. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ea1i Liverpool.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ea1i Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ea1i Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/11/13/thu-mon-alisson-nhan-xet-ve-phong-do.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ea1i Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nAnh th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 ch\u01b0a h\u1eb3n \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra su\u00f4n s\u1ebb nh\u01b0 mong \u0111\u1ee3i. \u201c<em>Nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u1edf m\u1ee9c v\u1eeba ph\u1ea3i</em>\u201d, Alisson n\u00f3i. \u201c<em>Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao d\u1ef1a theo ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n, v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n ph\u00ed k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n.</em>\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c<em>\u00c1p l\u1ef1c r\u1ea5t cao v\u00e0 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi lu\u00f4n mu\u1ed1n t\u00f4i tr\u1edf n\u00ean ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. T\u00f4i \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn c\u00f2n qu\u00e1 s\u1edbm \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i li\u1ec7u t\u00f4i c\u00f3 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng hay kh\u00f4ng. T\u00f4i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 h\u01a1n.</em>\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c<em>T\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m song t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n trong ngh\u1ec1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c thay \u0111\u1ed5i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, thay \u0111\u1ed5i th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1, gia \u0111\u00ecnh t\u00f4i v\u1eabn \u0111ang r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac. T\u00f4i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 Liverpool v\u00e0 \u0110T Brazil ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n.</em>\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Liverpool tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-liverpool-vs-fulham-172-202068.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/11/12/143729-2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-liverpool-vs-fulham-172-202068.html\">Liverpool h\u1ea1 \u0111\u1eb9p Fulham: Jurgen Klopp v\u00e0 th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m\u2026 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eddi</span><br>\r\n<span>Sau c\u00fa ng\u00e3 ng\u1ef1a mu\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t \u1edf Champions League, The Kop c\u1ea7n nhanh ch\u00f3ng g\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u1eady tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngay cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh...</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-20-fulham-mai-nha-anfield-nang-buoc-lu-doan-do-172-202044.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2